---
import Layout from '../layout/Layout.astro';
import MemberToggle from '../components/MemberToggle';
import PriceCalculator from '../components/PriceCalculator';

// SEO Meta
const title = "Pricing | Laundry Pickup & Delivery in Detroit | Bags of Laundry";
const description = "Simple, transparent pricing from Bags of Laundry. $2.25/lb standard, $1.99/lb with membership. $35 minimum, rush & add-ons available. Start your order today.";
---

<Layout title={title} description={description}>
  <main>
    {/* CORE PRICING */}
    <section class="py-8 sm:py-12 lg:py-20 bg-brand-bg">
      <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
        <h2 class="section-title text-center text-brand-text mb-4 sm:mb-6">Per-pound pricing</h2>

        <MemberToggle client:load onToggle={(isMember) => {}} />

        <div class="text-center">
          <div class="inline-block bg-gradient-to-r from-brand-primary to-brand-accent px-6 py-3 rounded-2xl mb-6 shadow-lg">
            <h3 class="font-bold text-lg text-black">âœ¨ All per-pound orders include:</h3>
          </div>
          <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-3 gap-4 sm:gap-6 max-w-4xl mx-auto">
            <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-4 shadow-sm border border-gray-100 hover:shadow-md transition-shadow">
              <div class="text-2xl mb-2">ðŸšš</div>
              <div class="font-semibold text-brand-text text-sm sm:text-base">Free pickup & delivery</div>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-4 shadow-sm border border-gray-100 hover:shadow-md transition-shadow">
              <div class="text-2xl mb-2">ðŸ‘•</div>
              <div class="font-semibold text-brand-text text-sm sm:text-base">Professional wash & fold</div>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-4 shadow-sm border border-gray-100 hover:shadow-md transition-shadow">
              <div class="text-2xl mb-2">ðŸ’°</div>
              <div class="font-semibold text-brand-text text-sm sm:text-base">$35 minimum order</div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    {/* BAG PRICING */}
    <section class="py-8 sm:py-12 lg:py-20 bg-white">
      <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
        <h2 class="section-title text-center text-brand-text mb-4 sm:mb-6">Per bag pricing</h2>
        <p class="text-center text-gray-500 mb-8 sm:mb-12 text-sm sm:text-base">Fixed pricing regardless of weight within capacity limitsâ€”<strong class="text-brand-text">bags must close</strong> for fair pricing.</p>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6 sm:gap-8">

          <article class="card overflow-hidden">
            <div class="w-full h-48 overflow-hidden" style="aspect-ratio: 1 / 1;">
              <img
                src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1553062407-98eeb64c6a62?q=80&w=600&auto=format&fit=crop"
                alt="Small laundry bag"
                class="w-full h-full object-cover"
              />
            </div>
            <div class="p-4 sm:p-6 text-center">
            <h3 class="text-lg sm:text-xl font-bold text-brand-text mb-2">Small Bag</h3>
            <p class="mb-2">
              <span class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-black text-brand-text">$35</span>
            </p>
            <p class="text-gray-500 mb-3 sm:mb-4 text-sm sm:text-base">Fits 12â€“18 lbs</p>
            <p class="text-gray-500 text-xs sm:text-sm mb-4 sm:mb-6">Perfect for individuals or light loads. One fixed price regardless of actual weight within limits.</p>
            <a href="/schedule?bag=small" class="btn-alt w-full text-center">Choose Small Bag</a>
            </div>
          </article>

          <article class="card overflow-hidden">
            <div class="relative">
              <div class="w-full h-48 overflow-hidden" style="aspect-ratio: 1 / 1;">
                <img
                  src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1582735689369-4fe89db7114c?q=80&w=600&auto=format&fit=crop"
                  alt="Medium laundry bag"
                  class="w-full h-full object-cover"
                />
              </div>
              <div class="absolute top-4 left-4 bg-orange-100 text-brand-primaryDeep border border-orange-200 rounded-full px-3 py-1 text-xs font-bold">
                Most Popular
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="p-4 sm:p-6 text-center">
            <h3 class="text-lg sm:text-xl font-bold text-brand-text mb-2">Medium Bag</h3>
            <p class="mb-2">
              <span class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-black text-brand-text">$55</span>
            </p>
            <p class="text-gray-500 mb-3 sm:mb-4 text-sm sm:text-base">Fits 20â€“30 lbs</p>
            <p class="text-gray-500 text-xs sm:text-sm mb-4 sm:mb-6">Great for families and regular laundry loads. Fixed pricing with generous capacity limits.</p>
            <a href="/schedule?bag=medium" class="btn-alt w-full text-center">Choose Medium Bag</a>
            </div>
          </article>

          <article class="card overflow-hidden">
            <div class="w-full h-48 overflow-hidden" style="aspect-ratio: 1 / 1;">
              <img
                src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1567538096630-e0c55bd6374c?q=80&w=600&auto=format&fit=crop"
                alt="Large laundry bag"
                class="w-full h-full object-cover"
              />
            </div>
            <div class="p-4 sm:p-6 text-center">
            <h3 class="text-lg sm:text-xl font-bold text-brand-text mb-2">Large Bag</h3>
            <p class="mb-2">
              <span class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-black text-brand-text">$85</span>
            </p>
            <p class="text-gray-500 mb-3 sm:mb-4 text-sm sm:text-base">Fits 35â€“45 lbs</p>
            <p class="text-gray-500 text-xs sm:text-sm mb-4 sm:mb-6">Best for large households or bulk loads. Fixed price with our largest capacity allowance.</p>
            <a href="/schedule?bag=large" class="btn-alt w-full text-center">Choose Large Bag</a>
            </div>
          </article>
        </div>
        <p class="text-xs text-gray-500 text-center mt-8">Open-bag / overstuffed fee: $10 (we'll text first). Bag capacity estimates vary by fabric and size.</p>
      </div>
    </section>

    {/* SPECIALTY SERVICES */}
    <section class="py-8 sm:py-12 lg:py-20 bg-brand-bg">
      <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
        <h2 class="section-title text-center text-brand-text mb-4 sm:mb-6">Specialty services</h2>
        <p class="text-center text-gray-500 mb-8 sm:mb-12 text-sm sm:text-base">Professional care for special items and fabrics</p>

        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-6 sm:gap-8 max-w-4xl mx-auto">
          <article class="card p-4 sm:p-6">
            <h3 class="text-lg sm:text-xl font-bold text-brand-text mb-2">Dry Cleaning</h3>
            <p class="mb-2">
              <span class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-black text-brand-text">From $8</span>
              <span class="text-xs sm:text-sm font-semibold text-gray-500 ml-1">per item</span>
            </p>
            <p class="text-gray-500 mb-3 sm:mb-4 text-sm sm:text-base">Expert care for suits, dresses, coats, delicates, and special fabrics requiring dry cleaning.</p>
            <p class="text-xs sm:text-sm text-gray-500">24-48 hour turnaround â€¢ $35 minimum order</p>
          </article>

          <article class="card p-4 sm:p-6">
            <h3 class="text-lg sm:text-xl font-bold text-brand-text mb-2">Bedding Bundle</h3>
            <p class="mb-2">
              <span class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-black text-brand-text">From $20</span>
              <span class="text-xs sm:text-sm font-semibold text-gray-500 ml-1">per bundle</span>
            </p>
            <p class="text-gray-500 mb-3 sm:mb-4 text-sm sm:text-base">Complete bedding sets, comforters, and bulky items. Specialized care for your bedding.</p>
            <p class="text-xs sm:text-sm text-gray-500">24 hour turnaround â€¢ $35 minimum order</p>
          </article>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    {/* ADD-ONS & FEES */}
    <section class="py-8 sm:py-12 lg:py-20 bg-white">
      <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
        <h2 class="section-title text-center text-brand-text mb-8 sm:mb-12">Pricing details</h2>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6 sm:gap-8">

          <div class="card p-4 sm:p-6">
            <h3 class="text-lg sm:text-xl font-bold text-brand-text mb-3 sm:mb-4">Add-ons</h3>
            <ul class="text-gray-500 space-y-2 text-sm sm:text-base">
              <li>â€¢ Eco-friendly detergent <strong class="text-brand-text">+$0.10/lb</strong></li>
              <li>â€¢ Hang-dry delicates <strong class="text-brand-text">+$0.25/lb</strong></li>
              <li>â€¢ Same-day rush <strong class="text-brand-text">+$10 or +$0.25/lb</strong></li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <div class="card p-4 sm:p-6">
            <h3 class="text-lg sm:text-xl font-bold text-brand-text mb-3 sm:mb-4">Minimums & fees</h3>
            <ul class="text-gray-500 space-y-2 text-sm sm:text-base">
              <li>â€¢ Order minimum <strong class="text-brand-text">$35</strong></li>
              <li>â€¢ Missed pickup window <strong class="text-brand-text">$7</strong></li>
              <li>â€¢ Open-bag / overstuffed <strong class="text-brand-text">$10</strong></li>
              <li>â€¢ Extended zone (if applicable) <strong class="text-brand-text">$3â€“5</strong></li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <div class="card p-4 sm:p-6">
            <h3 class="text-lg sm:text-xl font-bold text-brand-text mb-3 sm:mb-4">What's included</h3>
            <ul class="text-gray-500 space-y-2 text-sm sm:text-base">
              <li>â€¢ Free pickup & delivery</li>
              <li>â€¢ Sorting by color/fabric</li>
              <li>â€¢ Visible stain pretreat</li>
              <li>â€¢ Neat fold or garment press</li>
              <li>â€¢ Text updates & photo proof</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    {/* PRICE CALCULATOR */}
    <section class="py-8 sm:py-12 lg:py-20 bg-brand-bg">
      <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
        <h2 class="section-title text-center text-brand-text mb-4 sm:mb-6">Quick estimate</h2>
        <p class="text-center text-gray-500 mb-8 sm:mb-12 text-sm sm:text-base">Enter your best guess in pounds â€” an average family load is ~8â€“12 lb. This isn't a quote; exact totals show at checkout.</p>

        <PriceCalculator client:load isMember={false} />
      </div>
    </section>

    {/* COMMERCIAL PRICING */}
    <section class="py-8 sm:py-12 lg:py-20 bg-white">
      <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
        <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-8 sm:gap-12 items-start">

          <div>
            <h2 class="section-title text-brand-text mb-4 sm:mb-6">Commercial pricing</h2>
            <p class="text-gray-500 mb-4 sm:mb-6 leading-relaxed text-sm sm:text-base">
              Running an Airbnb portfolio, gym, spa, restaurant, or clinic? We build simple, volume-based quotes with dedicated pickup windows and delivery manifests.
            </p>
            <ul class="text-gray-500 mb-6 sm:mb-8 space-y-2 pl-4 text-sm sm:text-base">
              <li>â€¢ Recurring routes (weekly or multi-week)</li>
              <li>â€¢ Inventory counts & bag barcodes</li>
              <li>â€¢ Preferred turnaround & rush capacity</li>
            </ul>
            <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-3 sm:gap-4">
              <a href="/contact" class="btn w-full sm:w-auto">Talk to Sales</a>
              <a href="/service-areas" class="btn-alt w-full sm:w-auto">Check Coverage</a>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div>
            <div class="overflow-x-auto">
              <table class="w-full border border-gray-200 rounded-xl overflow-hidden">
                <thead>
                  <tr class="bg-orange-50">
                    <th class="p-2 sm:p-4 text-left text-xs sm:text-sm font-bold text-brand-text">Approx. weekly volume</th>
                    <th class="p-2 sm:p-4 text-left text-xs sm:text-sm font-bold text-brand-text">Indicative rate</th>
                    <th class="p-2 sm:p-4 text-left text-xs sm:text-sm font-bold text-brand-text">Notes</th>
                  </tr>
                </thead>
                <tbody class="text-xs sm:text-sm">
                  <tr class="border-t border-gray-200">
                    <td class="p-2 sm:p-4 text-brand-text">50â€“100 lb</td>
                    <td class="p-2 sm:p-4 text-brand-text">$2.05â€“$2.15/lb</td>
                    <td class="p-2 sm:p-4 text-gray-500">Standard next-day</td>
                  </tr>
                  <tr class="border-t border-gray-200">
                    <td class="p-2 sm:p-4 text-brand-text">100â€“250 lb</td>
                    <td class="p-2 sm:p-4 text-brand-text">$1.90â€“$2.05/lb</td>
                    <td class="p-2 sm:p-4 text-gray-500">Route day required</td>
                  </tr>
                  <tr class="border-t border-gray-200">
                    <td class="p-2 sm:p-4 text-brand-text">250+ lb</td>
                    <td class="p-2 sm:p-4 text-brand-text">Custom</td>
                    <td class="p-2 sm:p-4 text-gray-500">Dedicated windows</td>
                  </tr>
                </tbody>
              </table>
            </div>
            <p class="text-xs text-gray-500 mt-3 sm:mt-4">Final pricing depends on mix (towels/linens), bagging, and turnaround needs.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    {/* FAQ */}
    <section class="py-8 sm:py-12 lg:py-20 bg-brand-bg">
      <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
        <h2 class="section-title text-center text-brand-text mb-8 sm:mb-12">Pricing FAQ</h2>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-4 sm:gap-6">

          <div class="card p-4 sm:p-6">
            <h3 class="text-base sm:text-lg font-bold text-brand-text mb-2 sm:mb-3">How does membership work?</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-500 text-sm sm:text-base">Members get $1.99/lb pricing (vs $2.25/lb standard) with weekly or bi-weekly recurring pickups. Save $0.26 per pound on every order.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="card p-4 sm:p-6">
            <h3 class="text-base sm:text-lg font-bold text-brand-text mb-2 sm:mb-3">Why do you have a $35 minimum?</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-500 text-sm sm:text-base">Each pickup has fixed costs (driver time, routing, supplies). The minimum keeps pricing fair for small loads while maintaining quality service.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="card p-4 sm:p-6">
            <h3 class="text-base sm:text-lg font-bold text-brand-text mb-2 sm:mb-3">Can I switch between per-pound and bag pricing?</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-500 text-sm sm:text-base">Absolutelyâ€”choose whatever pricing works better for your load that day. No commitment required.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="card p-4 sm:p-6">
            <h3 class="text-base sm:text-lg font-bold text-brand-text mb-2 sm:mb-3">How accurate is the estimator?</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-500 text-sm sm:text-base">It's designed to help you budget. Your final total is based on actual weight and options chosen at checkout.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    {/* FINAL CTA */}
    <section class="py-8 sm:py-12 lg:py-20 bg-white">
      <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
        <div class="card p-6 sm:p-8 lg:p-12 text-center">
          <h2 class="section-title text-brand-text mb-3 sm:mb-4">Ready to skip laundry day?</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-500 mb-6 sm:mb-8 text-sm sm:text-base">Book a pickup in minutes. We'll handle the rest.</p>
          <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row justify-center gap-3 sm:gap-4">
            <a href="/start-basic" class="btn w-full sm:w-auto">Schedule Pickup</a>
            <a href="/services" class="btn-alt w-full sm:w-auto">Explore Services</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
</Layout>
